---
title: "SSD UC1 — Generate Story from Text Prompt"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC1 — Generate Story from Text Prompt

    User->>S: makeNewSale()
    User->>S: selectMode(mode: "simple")
    S-->>User: modeConfirmed, availableGenres[]

    User->>S: setStoryOptions(genre, style, length)
    S-->>User: optionsConfirmed

    User->>S: submitPrompt(promptText)
    S-->>User: promptReceived, promptType

    alt promptType = "invalid" OR "nonsense"
        S-->>User: error("Invalid prompt")
    end

    loop system generating story
        S-->>User: progressUpdate(stage, message)
    end

    S-->>User: storyGenerated(storyId, title, scenes[], pdfPath)
